nodes.text: A High Priest of Dim-U was a member of the Bounty Hunters' Guild during Cradossk's tenure as guildmaster. Ro-San Borokki, the Guild's Director of Training, praised both his use of a crossbow and his ability to convince fellow religious beings to turn themselves in.
At some point after Cradossk's death, the High Priest of Dim-U went rogue and was last seen on Agamar. Boba Fett noted that his current bounty was 65,000 credits.
